content:
@everyone  

**NEW CONTENT**
-Political simulation  - votes, political parties and the parliament
-New technology sector UI transformation

@everyone  

I'm sure each of you asked yourself "Why I cant bomb hospitals ? or even schools or parks ?"
So now you can !

**New content from the war mechanics **

You can send jets to province to accomplish multiple missions
1. Close Air Support (CAS) - when you want to assist your land units during a battle on province
2. Clean Province Skies - intercept every incoming enemy jets or existing enemy jets on province (very affective on jets while they on CAS mission)
3. Bomb Military Infrastructures - See attachments for all existing options 
4. Bomb Civilian Infrastructures - See attachments for all existing options
5. Eliminate Defense System - Each province have two type of defense systems (Anti-Air, Anti-Missiles) when initializing this mission jets will target those defense systems and try to eliminate many as they can (required high electronic warfare attribute)
6. Mass Destruction Bombing - Land nuclear \ biochemical bomb on province

Thank you all again for your support !
I'm really excited from the upcoming Early Access 🙂

@everyone The first screenshots from the war mechanics !

Thanks again for your support and hope you'll like it 🙂

@everyone  The first footage from space !

The solar system

You'll be able to explore more galaxies and planets as you make progress in the game !

All planets and galaxies will be open to explore within your camera so you will be able to zoom at planets see actual satellites in orbits and even follow probes and spaceships to their location in real space environment !!

Hope you'll like it 🙂

**How you can get access to alpha or beta version of World Warfare & Economics:**

1. Win or place high in any of the competitions that we have going. Currently we have 3 competitions, they are the following:
A) **The DISBOARD Competition:** Win beta access and 20% discount by bumping the server 70 times in <#899706526544040018> channel.
B) **The Invite Competition:** Win alpha access by placing top 3 in this competition, you can win beta access by placing 4th to 10th place in this competition, read <#898081028705497169> for more info on rewards for this competition!
C) **The Activity Competition:** Win beta access by placing top 3 in this competition.

2. You can get alpha and beta access by becoming localization testers (translators), current localization testers are:
🇬🇧 English Localization Testers: <@!736331592754004070> & <@!624381956188274699> & <@!298964908937314306> 
🇪🇸 Spanish Localization Testers: <@!409036237421281290> & <@!302525184341049344> & <@!758041545122512988>
🇫🇷 French Localization Testers: <@!640533881166233622> & <@!306436026094583809> & <@!306826091627020298>
🇩🇪 German Localization Testers: <@!298497498605944853> & <@!261497114931101697>
🇷🇺 Russian Localization Testers: <@!481196605308010506> & 1 spot open.

As you can see we need one Russian translator! 

3. You can donate either **$2** or **$5** on Patreon, rewards for the two different Patreon tiers are:
A) **$2 tier:**
- Includes Discord benefits
- General support
- Exclusive voting power
- Promise your spot on beta version
B) **$5 tier:**
- Includes Discord benefits
- General support
- Exclusive voting power
- Promise your spot on beta version
- Early access on full game version (1 month before full game)
- 20% discount on purchasing the game @here
